---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Open Call | House Gallery">
  <main class="layout">
    <h1>Open Call</h1>

    <article class="open_call_exhibition">
      <h2>Your Least Favorite Work</h2>
      <p>This is a description about the show and what not.</p>

      <section class="details">
        <h3>Details</h3>
        <p><b>Size: </b>Not toooo big please.</p>
        <p><b>Medium: </b>Really anything</p>
        <p><b>Content: </b>Fan art frowned upon, nudity is okay (opening is not 18+ so keep that in mind.)
        <p><b>Submission delivery: </b>Mail or drop-off with appoitment <a href="mailto:thisisahousegallery@gmail.com">(contact us)</a></p>
        <p><b>Submission dates: </b>Gallery must receive work by July 10th</p>
      </section>

      <a class="cta" target="_blank" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeAXU7XeqjlyWrvz3lx5VZRW4_Mq9wbQUJO6D8WE7V3iyIVvg/viewform?usp=sf_link">
        <button>Submission Form</button>
      </a>

      <br></br>
      <section class="faq">
        <h3>FAQ</h3>
        <details>
          <summary>How will my work be installed?</summary>
          <p>If hardware is not installed on the piece we will use non-piercing methods such as handing clips or magents. If you do not want hardware touching the imagery, leave a border on your canvas.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Can I sell my art?</summary>
          <p>Sure, why not, include your price in the submission form. We won't charge any comissions either.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>When is the opening and how long will the show run?</summary>
          <p>The opening is on the first day the show starts. Check the <a href="/schedule">schedule</a> for these dates.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Where do I mail or drop off my art?</summary>
          <p>361 Lester Ave, Oakland CA 94606 - If you want to coordinate a person-to-person hand-off, email us at <a href="mailto:thisisahousegallery@gmail.com">thisisahousegallery@gmail.com</a></p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Can I submit more than one piece?</summary>
          <p>You can submit as many as you like but we'll only select 1-3</p>
        </details>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
	main {
		margin: auto;
    padding: var(--space-base-huge) var(--space-base-large) var(--space-base-large) var(--space-base-large);
    max-width: 1024px;

    @media (max-width: 675px) {
      padding: var(--space-base-medium) var(--space-base-small) var(--space-base-small) var(--space-base-small);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      padding: var(--space-base-large) var(--space-base-medium) var(--space-base-medium) var(--space-base-medium);
    }
	}

  .open_call_exhibition {
    border-top: 1px solid black;
    & .cta {
      text-decoration: underline;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  }
</style>
